4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Course that focuses on teaching web development skills and technologies. The course aims to help students build applications from scratch and become web development experts. It is a part-time course that lasts for 18 weeks. The program covers in-demand skills such as Python and JavaScript, as well as front-end libraries and API consumption. Students will also have the opportunity to develop and present their own project. The course does not require any previous coding skills or advanced math knowledge. Both English and Spanish options are available for the syllabus and content. Graduates of the course receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. The program is designed to prepare students for a career in the tech industry. For more information and to enroll, visit their website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop